<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2011-12-31</DATELINE><TITLE>Thoughts on Intervention in HIV/AIDS with Traditional Chinese Medicine</TITLE><BODY>Abstracts HIV/AIDS has become a worldwide pandemic and highly active antiretroviral therapy (HAART) is the only generally recognized effective therapy at present. However, various unresolvable problems appear with the widespread use of HAART. Traditional Chinese Medicine shows good efficacy for intervention in HIV/AIDS and could become an effective treatment option.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>